---
import IconBrandInstagram from "./icons/IconBrandInstagram.astro";
import IconBrandLinkedin from "./icons/IconBrandLinkedin.astro";
import IconBrandWhatsapp from "./icons/IconBrandWhatsapp.astro";
---

<section
  id="contacto"
  class="px-6 py-24 text-center text-offwhite"
  aria-labelledby="titulo-contacto"
>
  <h2
    id="titulo-contacto"
    class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-deco text-gold mb-6"
  >
    ¿Listo para potenciar tu marca?
  </h2>

  <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-[#ddd] max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
    Contactanos y descubrí cómo podemos transformar tu presencia digital.
    Respondemos siempre en el día.
  </p>

  <a
    href="mailto:studiodelfos11@gmail.com"
    class="inline-block bg-[#192e38] hover:bg-gold hover:text-black text-white font-medium px-8 py-3 rounded-full transition mb-10 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold"
    aria-label="Enviar email a Delfos Studio"
  >
    Escribinos
  </a>

  <div
    class="flex justify-center gap-6 mb-6"
    role="navigation"
    aria-label="Redes sociales Delfos Studio"
  >
    <a
      href="https://instagram.com/delfosstudio"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      aria-label="Instagram"
      title="Instagram"
      class="text-offwhite hover:text-gold transition text-2xl focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold"
    >
      <IconBrandInstagram class="w-6 h-6" />
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://linkedin.com/company/delfosstudio"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      aria-label="LinkedIn"
      title="LinkedIn"
      class="text-offwhite hover:text-gold transition text-2xl focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold"
    >
      <IconBrandLinkedin class="w-6 h-6" />
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://wa.me/+5492324592391"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      aria-label="WhatsApp"
      title="WhatsApp"
      class="text-offwhite hover:text-gold transition text-2xl focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold"
    >
      <IconBrandWhatsapp class="w-6 h-6" />
    </a>
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm text-[#888] max-w-md mx-auto">
    También podés encontrarnos en redes sociales o agendar una videollamada
    cuando quieras.
  </p>
</section>
